# Movie CRUD API URLs

Base URL:
http://localhost:9090

1. Add Movie
POST http://localhost:9090/movie
Comment: Adds a new movie to the system.

2. Get All Movies
GET http://localhost:9090/movies
Comment: Retrieves the list of all movies.

3. Get Movie By ID
GET http://localhost:9090/movie/{id}
Example: GET http://localhost:9090/movie/1
Comment: Fetches a movie using its ID.

4. Update Movie
PUT http://localhost:9090/movie/{id}
Example: PUT http://localhost:9090/movie/1
Comment: Updates the details of an existing movie.

5. Delete Movie
DELETE http://localhost:9090/movie/{id}
Example: DELETE http://localhost:9090/movie/1
Comment: Deletes the movie with the given ID.